    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment for the VAD hemolysis CFD model at MRL 5 has been reviewed. Seven factors were assessed and six remain not-assessed. The assessed factors demonstrate achieved levels below required levels across the board. Monte Carlo UQ was completed for geometric uncertainty. The package is accepted for submission pending resolution of open factor gaps.",
